00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,040
I don't get it.

290
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:45,000
Just remember,

291
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:47,240
Third Master not returning home right now

292
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,300
is also to spare Madam from worrying.

293
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:50,270
After all,

294
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,080
this plan of ours

295
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:54,670
was kept a secret from Madam as well.

296
00:16:04,790 --> 00:16:08,290
[Linxia Restaurant]

297
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,550
It's been a few days.

298
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:11,290
Why hasn't brother-in-law returned yet?

299
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,240
Can we not talk about this nonsense?

300
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,920
I heard you caught a chill a few days ago.

301
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:21,240
Your complexion still doesn't look good.

302
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,910
You should rest well at home.

303
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,570
Why did you have to come?

304
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:26,960
Some matters

305
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,580
should be settled
sooner rather than later.

306
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,030
It's better

307
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:33,950
to do it here than at home.

308
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,080
Sister Jinzhao.

309
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,290
What exactly happened?

310
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:44,590
Why suddenly break off the engagement?

311
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,320
Sit down.

312
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:01,550
What did

313
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,470
your father tell you?

314
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,960
Father only said there would be
no marriage.

315
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:06,720
He didn't say

316
00:17:07,109 --> 00:17:09,040
a single word about anything else.

317
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,220
I went to see Xuanqing once,

318
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,770
but he refused to see me.

319
00:17:13,109 --> 00:17:14,480
Father found out later

320
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,589
and scolded me.

321
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,310
He forbade me from seeing Xuanqing again.

322
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:20,550
If you hadn't sent someone
to pick me up today,

323
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:22,609
Father wouldn't have allowed me out.

324
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,829
I asked you here today

325
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,680
because I wanted

326
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:29,210
to explain this matter to you
face to face.

327
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,830
You heard

328
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:32,560
what Xuanqing said that day

329
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,810
at Lan's residence.

330
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,070
After weighing the pros and cons,

331
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:36,960
Third Master,

332
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,510
your father, and I

333
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,140
feel that you and Xuanqing

334
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,570
are not a good match.

335
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,200
It's you!

336
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:53,360
The person in Xuanqing's heart...

337
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,110
It's you, isn't it?

338
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:07,980
I actually guessed it a long time ago.

339
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,840
That day, Xuanqing

340
00:18:10,890 --> 00:18:12,550
seemed to be talking to me.

341
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:17,540
But he was clearly looking at you
the whole time.

342
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,830
I knew then

343
00:18:21,290 --> 00:18:23,190
he wasn't being honest with me.

344
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:25,880
He was using me

345
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,610
to express his feelings to you.

346
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,880
That's why the engagement was broken off.

347
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,590
Wanxue,

348
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:33,480
you should find someone

349
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:35,280
who knows you, understands you,

350
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:37,310
-and truly loves you.
-What's the use of saying

351
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:38,310
these things now?

352
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,640
I clearly told you

353
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:45,030
that I've had feelings for Xuanqing
since we were little.

354
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:46,050
I even said

355
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:46,920
that no matter what,

356
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,450
I'd be willing to marry him.

357
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,680
And you have already

358
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,920
married Third Uncle.

359
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:52,240
Why did you have to

360
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,680
expose all of this?

361
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,680
Couldn't we just live our own lives?

362
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:58,320
Wouldn't that be better?

363
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,480
You can't

364
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:00,480
knowingly

365
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,310
jump into a fire pit.

366
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:08,200
Do you still have feelings for Xuanqing?

367
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,000
Of course not.

368
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:10,270
Then could you

369
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,380
talk to Uncle Chen

370
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,240
and ask him not to
call off the engagement?

371
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:13,830
No.

372
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,480
Xuanqing will soon

373
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:17,880
be transferred away,

374
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,680
and won't return to the capital.

375
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,520
Just forget him.

376
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:45,460
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

377
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:47,650
Are you willing

378
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,680
to be with me?

379
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:52,390
When we encounter a problem,

380
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,240
don't be in a hurry to back down.

381
00:19:55,230 --> 00:19:56,230
Let's see if we can

382
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:57,950
come up with a better way

383
00:19:58,440 --> 00:19:59,310
to solve it.

384
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,640
You once said

385
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,590
we'd face things

386
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:05,040
and solve them together.

387
00:20:05,790 --> 00:20:06,790
And now?

388
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:16,570
I want to be calm and rational too,

389
00:20:17,130 --> 00:20:17,940
but I...

390
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,510
Since you are hiding

391
00:20:39,530 --> 00:20:40,990
and avoiding me like this,

392
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:44,290
I'll have to be ruthless
and force your hand.

393
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:46,740
Let's see if you really intend

394
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:48,030
never to look back.

395
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:10,460
[Chen Yanyun] [Gu Jinzhao]

396
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,630
[Chen Yanyun] [Gu Jinzhao]

397
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:22,100
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

398
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:30,000
Take this

399
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,400
to Chen Yi

400
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,150
and have him give it to Third Master.

401
00:21:34,150 --> 00:21:36,620
[To Third Master]

402
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:36,550
My Lady,

403
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,860
is this really necessary?

404
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,960
Maybe we should wait a little longer.

405
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,790
I have already

406
00:21:42,110 --> 00:21:43,310
waited for many days.

407
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:45,560
I don't want to wait anymore.

408
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,940
Since he clearly knows

409
00:21:48,070 --> 00:21:49,000
I'm not at fault,

410
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,940
yet still makes things difficult for me,

411
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:54,200
I naturally won't indulge him either.

412
00:21:56,790 --> 00:21:57,550
Yes.

413
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,480
Third Master.

414
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:23,960
Everything is ready?

415
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:24,680
Yes, it's ready.

416
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,210
Let's go.

417
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,160
Oh right, Third Master.

418
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:28,360
Qingpu brought this,

419
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,590
a letter for you from Madam.

420
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:30,110
Madam?

421
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:30,550
Yes.

422
00:22:31,730 --> 00:22:33,660
[To Third Master]

423
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:44,740
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

424
00:22:49,410 --> 00:22:54,660
[Letter of Amicable Separation]

425
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:00,200
♪ Once I wrote of spring and fall ♪

426
00:23:00,810 --> 00:23:03,850
♪ Yet fell through time's abyss ♪

427
00:23:06,190 --> 00:23:07,660
♪ Every shade turned bitter ♪

428
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:11,360
♪ Every longing became sorrow ♪

429
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,510
♪ I've seen through right and wrong ♪

430
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:19,760
♪ Old vows washed away like ash ♪

431
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:26,920
♪ True devotion is knowing
the freedom within your heart♪

432
00:23:27,930 --> 00:23:30,770
♪ Word by word, hand in hand ♪

433
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:34,480
♪ My heart grows cold like rust ♪

434
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:38,510
♪ The stars send you far away ♪

435
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:41,870
♪ Yet one thought still remains ♪

436
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:46,350
♪ You share bright days with another ♪

437
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:50,120
♪ I walk with my lonely shadow ♪

438
00:23:51,000 --> 00:24:00,930
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

439
00:24:34,060 --> 00:24:36,050
[Linxia Restaurant]

440
00:24:47,810 --> 00:24:50,200
[Linxia Restaurant]

441
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:00,900
Miss Zhao really knows
how to get things done.

442
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:02,160
She even managed to invite all the wives

443
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,270
of the Grand Secretaries.

444
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:06,200
We won't have to worry about our business
from now on.

445
00:25:06,610 --> 00:25:08,610
I'm not worried about the business.

446
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:10,720
I'm worried about my eldest sister.

447
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:24,760
This tea smells so good.

448
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,260
This is this year's

449
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,600
first flush of Songluo.

450
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:29,970
It was brewed with mountain spring water.

451
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,060
This pattern leaves some margin.

452
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:36,310
Madam, you can cut along

453
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:38,920
the outer edge of the pattern
along with the fabric.

454
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,640
As if I didn't know

455
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,440
I need to cut it with the pattern!

456
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:42,720
Exactly.

457
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,490
It's just a piece of fabric.

458
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,200
If it's ruined, it's ruined.

459
00:25:47,020 --> 00:25:48,960
What do you mean "if it's ruined,
it's ruined"?

460
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,550
Are you saying

461
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:50,810
I ruined it on purpose?

462
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:51,590
I...

463
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:53,710
We are cutting fabrics today

464
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:56,240
to imitate the Empress Dowager

465
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:59,590
and encourage the people
to plant mulberry trees.

466
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,680
But if we ruin too many fabrics,

467
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:04,310
it rather defeats the original purpose.

468
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:09,600
I actually have an idea.

469
00:26:10,670 --> 00:26:11,910
The ruined fabric

470
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:13,340
doesn't have to be thrown away.

471
00:26:13,340 --> 00:26:15,400
Have someone sew the pieces together

472
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,070
to make patched blessing clothes

473
00:26:17,070 --> 00:26:19,350
and donate them to the children
at the Hall of Benevolence.

474
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:20,790
That's a good idea.

475
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:24,000
Madam Chen is truly clever.

476
00:26:24,310 --> 00:26:25,370
Now that you say it,

477
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:27,440
we don't feel burdened anymore.

478
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,340
In my opinion,

479
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:33,340
Madam Chen's cleverness is only secondary.

480
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:36,270
What matters most is her composure.

481
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,260
If it were anyone else,

482
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:40,960
with their Second Uncle
dismissed from office

483
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:43,200
and their ancestral home
losing half its assets,

484
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:45,070
they would have cried themselves to death.

485
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:46,230
But Madam Chen

486
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:48,090
remains calm and collected,

487
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:49,680
even enjoying tea here.

488
00:26:53,590 --> 00:26:55,440
My Second Uncle broke the law.

489
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:57,270
He deserved to be punished.

490
00:26:57,270 --> 00:26:59,070
What is there for me to cry about?

491
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,480
Well said.

492
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,880
Madam Chen really

493
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:04,480
has seen her share of storms.

494
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,030
I heard

495
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:07,920
when Madam Chen was little,

496
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:10,200
she was sent to her
maternal grandparents' house

497
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,270
because

498
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:12,640
her fate

499
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:15,880
was supposedly hindering
her father's official career.

500
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:18,410
I originally didn't believe in
these things.

501
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,940
But thinking about it now,

502
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,270
it's true.

503
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:22,880
Your father

504
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,590
was indeed demoted

505
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:25,990
and sent out to Pingyang.

506
00:27:26,510 --> 00:27:28,110
This time, your Second Uncle

507
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:29,400
was also dismissed.

508
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:31,030
Could it be that

509
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:32,870
this fortune-telling stuff

510
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,400
actually makes sense?

511
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,720
Madam Chen,

512
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,640
you must be careful.

513
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:41,420
It's one thing if it's your father
and uncle,

514
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,970
but what if it affects Jiuheng?

515
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:49,510
Why are you saying all this?

516
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:53,160
I'm just joking.

517
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,000
Mrs. Wang

518
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,160
is deliberately causing trouble today,
isn't she?

519
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,590
She is just angry.

520
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:04,480
The investigation into the Gu Deyuan case
has reached this point.

521
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:05,590
Over thirty court officials

522
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:07,510
have been implicated
and thrown into prison.

523
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:08,600
However,

524
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:09,400
it hasn't involved Jiuheng

525
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,790
in the slightest.

526
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:13,000
But the matter of Wang Xuanfan

527
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:14,830
colluding with the late Prince Chengqing

528
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:16,760
is becoming more and more evident.

529
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,400
I heard

530
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:19,350
they have already found the family

531
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:21,350
of the concubine who died suddenly.

532
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,310
My Lady!

533
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,510
My Lady!

534
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:31,760
What's wrong?

535
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,400
Today, Third Master

536
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,080
went to Mount Yu to inspect Dingling tomb

537
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:36,080
and was ambushed.

538
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,240
My Lady!

539
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:50,270
I was right, wasn't I?

540
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,460
What are you doing?

541
00:28:59,240 --> 00:28:59,720
You...

542
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,710
If our Master

543
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:05,460
has any mishap today,

544
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:07,210
I will hold you

545
00:29:07,230 --> 00:29:08,700
entirely responsible!

546
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:11,290
You will answer for him with your life!

547
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:46,030
Madam.

548
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,750
I am incompetent.

549
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,720
I failed to protect Third Master.

550
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:55,120
Please punish me, Madam!

551
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:08,310
My Lady!

552
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:30,920
Mother,

553
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,800
let's go back first.

554
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:35,470
Let my sister-in-law stay with Yanyun.

555
00:30:44,750 --> 00:30:46,270
Why are your hands so cold?

556
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,800
Third Master.

557
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,960
Because we left in a hurry,

558
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,890
Third Master only took me with him.

559
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:02,270
Shortly after leaving the capital,

560
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:04,240
we unexpectedly met assassins.

561
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,510
They outnumbered us,

562
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:08,160
and had archers ambushed in the woods.

563
00:31:11,110 --> 00:31:12,370
Do you suspect anyone?

564
00:31:13,030 --> 00:31:13,680
Yes.

565
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:17,270
The whole Court is talking about it.

566
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:19,950
They all say Wang Xuanfan

567
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:22,570
was caught with evidence by Third Master

568
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,180
and he hired assassins

569
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:27,040
to kill him in desperation.

570
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:33,730
[Wang Mansion]

571
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:34,100
I did not assassinate Third Mr. Chen!

572
00:31:33,850 --> 00:31:38,910
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

573
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:34,920
Master,

574
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,000
Lord Wang Shenzhi, Chief Justice

575
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,070
of the Imperial Court of Judicial Review,
is here.

576
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:40,160
He said he wanted to ask

577
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,640
about the assassination of

578
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,720
Lord Chen Yanyun.

579
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,680
Go tell him

580
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,240
that I don't know who

581
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,270
assassinated Chen Jiuheng.

582
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:49,000
But it definitely wasn't me.

583
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,240
Exactly!

584
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,920
Does he have evidence?

585
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:53,240
How dare he come asking?

586
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,240
From what he said,

587
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:56,240
it seems he might have evidence.

588
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:56,960
I...

589
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,430
I just received the news

590
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,310
that one of the men

591
00:31:59,310 --> 00:32:00,680
we sent to spy on Chen Yanyun

592
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,640
is missing.

593
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,000
You may leave now.

594
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:08,550
Yes.

595
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:20,440
Why are you looking at me like that?

596
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:21,920
Tell me the truth.

597
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:23,710
Did you do it?

598
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:25,880
It really wasn't me!

599
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:28,770
It's true

600
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:31,470
that I would love to kill Third Mr. Chen,

601
00:32:31,750 --> 00:32:33,680
but that breaks the rules.

602
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:35,110
A Grand Secretary assassinating another

603
00:32:35,110 --> 00:32:36,510
is unprecedented.

604
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:39,910
But everyone out there is saying

605
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,750
you were afraid Third Mr. Chen
would produce

606
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:43,830
evidence of your collusion
with Prince Chengqing,

607
00:32:43,830 --> 00:32:45,200
so you were backed into a corner
like a dog

608
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,030
and hired an assassin.

609
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:47,590
Who are you calling a dog?

610
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,270
I...

611
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:54,800
Everyone out?

612
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:58,830
No, no.

613
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,770
Someone is trying to frame me.

614
00:33:03,110 --> 00:33:03,910
Yes, yes, yes.

615
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:04,730
This...

616
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:06,750
This must be someone framing me!

617
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:08,350
Who would dare to frame you?

618
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:09,650
Third Mr. Chen?

619
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,070
I've asked around.

620
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:14,060
He really got shot by an arrow.

621
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,610
The injury is serious.

622
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:23,830
Could it be...

623
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,480
Could it be

624
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,760
the Senior Grand Secretary?

625
00:33:32,790 --> 00:33:33,520
Impossible.

626
00:33:34,350 --> 00:33:35,400
Absolutely impossible.

627
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:37,110
The Senior Grand Secretary still needs me.

628
00:33:37,110 --> 00:33:38,840
He will definitely protect me.

629
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:40,530
Third Mr. Chen's tricks

630
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:41,730
are useless.

631
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,400
Definitely useless.

632
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,320
Why are you crying like this?

633
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,670
Don't worry.

634
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:10,320
I won't die.

635
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,440
How can I not worry?

636
