You bled so much,

637
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,660
and were unconscious for so long.

638
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:25,040
It's my first time seeing you like this.

639
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:26,470
Don't ever

640
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:27,990
scare me like this again!

641
00:35:33,190 --> 00:35:34,590
How do you feel now?

642
00:35:36,150 --> 00:35:37,110
Just so-so.

643
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,640
Then rest yourself.

644
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:45,110
I won't disturb you anymore.

645
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,110
Come back!

646
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:57,370
Sit.

647
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:58,710
I won't sit!

648
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:01,110
Just say what you want to say.

649
00:36:04,710 --> 00:36:06,300
Why are you so stubborn?

650
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,220
Because you make me angry.

651
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:12,130
You were the one who wanted a divorce.

652
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,440
Why are you angry?

653
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,540
Why am I angry?

654
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:16,630
Chen Yanyun!

655
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:18,830
You have some nerve saying that!

656
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:20,210
Why did I want a divorce?

657
00:36:20,590 --> 00:36:22,190
It was all because you ignored me.

658
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:23,450
You treated me coldly,

659
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,760
staying in the Hall of Literary Profundity
all day

660
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:26,020
and never coming home!

661
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,400
It was you

662
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,670
who didn't want to be with me anymore,

663
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:30,130
yet you put the blame on me.

664
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,550
Are all you Grand Secretaries like this?

665
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:34,190
No wonder the people of Great Yan

666
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,450
are in dire suffering.

667
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:38,200
I didn't stay away from home
on purpose.

668
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:41,070
I was angry that you knew clearly

669
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,870
about Chen Xuanqing's treason,

670
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:44,320
yet...

671
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:49,000
