672
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,400
Tell you?

673
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:53,480
You tell me.

674
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,260
If you were in my shoes,

675
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,460
what would you say?

676
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,110
Just speak openly.

677
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:03,810
Say that you and Chen Xuanqing

678
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,280
