679
00:37:07,290 --> 00:37:08,870
No, it's a relationship.

680
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,030
Just say that you and Chen Xuanqing

681
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:12,160
had a relationship.

682
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,360
It started from the coming-of-age
ceremony,

683
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:18,110
and stopped abruptly
before the metropolitan examination.

684
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:19,920
That is a matter of the past.

685
00:37:20,670 --> 00:37:21,920
But Chen Xuanqing

686
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,530
keeps pestering you

687
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:24,960
