688
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,070
You can't do this.

689
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,080
You are being unreasonable.

690
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,930
Has being reasonable ever worked?

691
00:37:46,070 --> 00:37:47,630
Since you have investigated

692
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:48,190
