693
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:49,280
so clearly,

694
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,800
do I still need to be reasonable?

695
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,620
Would you even listen?

696
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:59,150
I know I shouldn't blame you.

697
00:38:00,630 --> 00:38:01,760
I am just angry

698
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,240
that you actually

699
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,840
pursued another man.

700
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,190
And that man wasn't me.

701
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,640
I'm angry at myself too,

702
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:12,530
for not realizing earlier

703
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:15,030
my feelings for you.

704
00:38:17,740 --> 00:38:19,590
♪ Ask the passing time
whether it has forgotten ♪

705
00:38:20,410 --> 00:38:21,920
♪ The moonlight of our first encounter ♪

706
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:26,660
♪ Year after year,
it etches your likeness ♪

707
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:29,770
♪ Count the faint shimmer
of the starry river ♪

708
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:34,590
♪ Yet none compares
to the gentle light in your eyes ♪

709
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:37,540
♪ At last, I see the galaxy
shimmering and swaying ♪

710
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:40,130
♪ Reflected in our eyes ♪

711
00:38:41,170 --> 00:38:45,660
♪ I'll be with you forever ♪

712
00:38:46,810 --> 00:38:50,460
♪ And enjoy
the beautiful scenery with you ♪

713
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:56,340
♪ For all the days of our lives,
our love will endure ♪

714
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,440
Where did you learn all this?

715
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:59,540
Directly from you, the Grand Secretary.

716
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,630
What's wrong? Does it hurt again?

717
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:04,090
I'll go get the physician.

718
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,060
Don't move.

719
00:39:06,930 --> 00:39:08,660
Let me hold you a little longer.

720
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:14,560
Third Master!

721
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:17,710
What is it?

722
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:18,920
The Court of Judicial Review,

723
00:39:18,920 --> 00:39:20,030
based on the clues we left,

724
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:21,230
