733
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:35,920
Yes.

734
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,030
So,

735
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,230
was this assassination really

736
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:42,630
the doing of Wang Xuanfan?

737
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:45,110
Truth and falsehood mix,

738
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,880
