739
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,960
what is real and what is fake.

740
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:53,170
You're being mysterious.

741
00:39:57,580 --> 00:40:00,130
[A Heart of Purity and Loftiness]

742
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,890
If you have anything to ask,

743
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:12,920
