746
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:21,010
I really can't hide anything from you.

747
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:23,250
So, it was actually faked?

748
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:26,880
Does it hurt again?

749
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,580
Oh, my dear.

750
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:31,400
The assassination was fake,

751
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:32,880
but the wound is real.

752
00:40:35,030 --> 00:40:36,050
You did this

753
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,870
