754
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,070
Wang Xuanfan and I

755
00:40:39,230 --> 00:40:40,680
are completely at odds.

756
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,000
He had people tail me,

757
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:44,130
which was already breaking the rules.

758
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,670
So I just played along

759
00:40:47,110 --> 00:40:48,310
and put on a full show.

760
00:40:49,590 --> 00:40:50,320
Since

761
00:40:50,510 --> 00:40:51,960
