763
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:55,670
It was all because you sent me

764
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:58,730
the Letter of Amicable Separation
this morning.

765
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:01,480
You saw the Letter of Amicable Separation

766
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:03,280
