767
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:05,060
I didn't want to live anymore.

768
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,190
What nonsense are you talking about?

769
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:07,920
I wanted a divorce,

770
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:09,120
