771
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:10,760
It hurts.

772
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:12,010
It hurts.

773
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:14,550
Does it hurt again?

774
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,670
It hurts.

775
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:23,010
Do you still want to divorce me?

776
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,340
No, I don't.

777
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,200
Third Master.

778
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:36,450
The Senior Grand Secretary
has arrived at the gate.

779
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:42,550
The Senior Grand Secretary...

780
00:41:42,550 --> 00:41:44,670
He probably didn't come
to see about your injury, did he?

781
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:45,600
Definitely not.

782
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,710
He is most likely here

783
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:49,550
to plead for Wang Xuanfan.

784
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:08,310
Another half inch,

785
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:10,130
and it would have hit the heart.

786
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:13,400
Lord Chen, you are indeed fortunate.

787
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,920
Glad you are fine.

788
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:19,000
I'll go write the prescription then.

789
00:42:21,630 --> 00:42:22,360
Come with me.

790
00:42:39,030 --> 00:42:39,720
I'm fine.

791
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:41,410
Please have a seat, Mentor.

792
00:42:43,630 --> 00:42:45,090
Imperial Physician Zhou,

793
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:46,510
in terms of treating external injuries,

794
00:42:46,510 --> 00:42:47,560
is unparalleled

795
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:48,480
in

796
00:42:49,230 --> 00:42:50,960
the Imperial Medical Academy.

797
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,290
I have worried you, Mentor.

798
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:58,960
Seeing you so seriously injured,

799
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:02,480
I'll get straight to the point

800
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:03,880
