803
00:43:12,320 --> 00:43:13,480
I heard that

804
00:43:14,150 --> 00:43:14,960
all the men

805
00:43:15,110 --> 00:43:16,920
Wang Xuanfan sent to watch me

806
00:43:17,030 --> 00:43:18,550
have been captured

807
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:19,480
and

808
00:43:20,510 --> 00:43:21,910
