809
00:43:27,510 --> 00:43:29,070
How much do you actually know

810
00:43:29,070 --> 00:43:31,280
about Wang Xuanfan's collusion

811
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:33,320
with the late Prince Chengqing?

812
00:43:34,150 --> 00:43:35,000
Actually,

813
00:43:35,670 --> 00:43:37,360
I wouldn't dare hide it from you, Mentor.

814
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:39,090
I truly don't know much either.

815
00:43:39,110 --> 00:43:40,110
What I said

816
00:43:40,110 --> 00:43:41,230
in Court back then

817
00:43:41,480 --> 00:43:43,480
was just a bluff to rattle Yuanweng.

818
00:43:43,630 --> 00:43:44,430
I thought that

819
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:45,920
if provoked,

820
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:48,000
he would definitely give himself away.

821
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:48,730
Sure enough,

822
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:51,960
he actually sent assassins

823
00:43:51,960 --> 00:43:53,110
to kill me.

824
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:56,450
A Grand Secretary assassinating
another Grand Secretary...

825
00:43:56,450 --> 00:43:58,540
Truly appalling.

826
00:43:59,920 --> 00:44:02,120
I couldn't believe it before either,

827
00:44:02,230 --> 00:44:04,670
but to bring down Fan Chuan, Yuanweng

828
00:44:05,110 --> 00:44:07,000
replaced the grain with bran,

829
00:44:07,360 --> 00:44:08,360
disregarding

830
00:44:08,590 --> 00:44:10,070
the lives of hundreds of thousands of
famine victims

831
00:44:10,070 --> 00:44:10,880
in Pingyang.

832
00:44:11,800 --> 00:44:12,960
Since then,

833
00:44:13,510 --> 00:44:14,510
I feel like

834
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:16,960
anything he does

835
00:44:17,510 --> 00:44:19,240
wouldn't surprise me anymore.

836
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:21,560
So about this matter,

837
00:44:21,630 --> 00:44:22,630
you still

838
00:44:22,880 --> 00:44:24,960
hold a grudge.

839
00:44:29,710 --> 00:44:31,400
But there was a reason.

840
00:44:32,070 --> 00:44:33,000
Doing this

841
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:35,260
makes you seem rather petty, doesn't it?

842
00:44:39,110 --> 00:44:41,280
Mentor, this summer is a bit long,

843
00:44:42,230 --> 00:44:44,230
and the summer flood is very severe.

844
00:44:45,230 --> 00:44:48,110
Officials from the River Conservancy Office
reported

845
00:44:48,110 --> 00:44:49,960
that in the lower reaches
of the Huaihe River,

846
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:51,620
there are a full twenty-three

847
00:44:51,710 --> 00:44:52,910
riverbank breaches.

848
00:44:53,230 --> 00:44:54,150
Yes.

849
00:44:56,110 --> 00:44:57,150
It's hard.

850
00:44:58,190 --> 00:44:59,780
Fifteen breaches

851
00:44:59,920 --> 00:45:02,070
were not caused by fierce floods

852
00:45:02,400 --> 00:45:04,260
or the river changing its course,

853
00:45:04,280 --> 00:45:05,190
but because of

854
00:45:05,710 --> 00:45:06,840
cutting corners

855
00:45:07,150 --> 00:45:08,480
