858
00:45:12,070 --> 00:45:12,920
Among them,

859
00:45:13,670 --> 00:45:15,870
the chief administrators in six places

860
00:45:15,880 --> 00:45:17,540
are Wang Xuanfan's students.

861
00:45:23,590 --> 00:45:25,710
